What Do I Need?
Open source version of breakout game
https://github.com/janbodnar/Java-Breakout-Game
Open source version of Pong Game
http://freesourcecode.net/javaprojects/15352/A-Pong-Game-in-Java#.YerUdOrMJaR
Open source version of Snake Game
https://github.com/janbodnar/Java-Snake-Game
Asteroids
https://github.com/caseyscarborough/j-asteroids

How to Modify the Games
Snake: Create a "Bad Apple" That reduces lenght of snake by one can randomly take the place of the normal apple
Breakout: Add a brick that can regenerate bricks arround it after being destroyed and add explosion brick causes dammage to surrounding bricks
Pong: Score is doubbled if player or AI can score twice in a row
Asteroids: Create a "Large Asteroid" That when destroyed creates two normal asteroids and if hit by asteroid game ends.
